Package com.example.flexiMed.model

Class AmbulanceEntity

java.lang.Object
com.example.flexiMed.model.AmbulanceEntity
@Entity public class AmbulanceEntity extends Object
Entity representing an ambulance in the system. It contains details such as plate number, driver information, location (latitude and longitude), availability status, and a timestamp of the last update.
